sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor U as User
participant FE as Frontend
participant AC as AuthController
participant AS as AuthService
participant DB as RefreshToken and User
participant JWT as JwtService

U->>FE: Session requires renewal
FE->>AC: POST /auth/refresh
AC->>AS: refresh(refreshToken)
AS->>DB: Find refresh token
alt Token is invalid or expired
  DB-->>AS: No valid token found
  AS-->>AC: Reject refresh
  AC-->>FE: 401 Unauthorized
  FE-->>U: Ask user to sign in again
else Token is valid
  DB-->>AS: Token and user data
  AS->>JWT: Generate new access token
  JWT-->>AS: Access token
  AS-->>AC: Refresh response
  AC-->>FE: 200 OK + accessToken
  FE-->>U: Continue current session
end
